  "texts": [
    "The last variable evaluated in the state-space for both the source and target controllers is the Outdoor air temperature, as it affects the operation and energy consumption of the cooling system and indoor temperature.",
    "The three variables added to the state-space for the target DRL controllers are the BESS SOC, PV energy production and the Building total electrical consumption.",
    "The Building total electrical consumption and PV energy production play a pivotal role in the optimal management of the controlled system.",
    "Moreover, the information related to the PV operation is provided to the agent from the current control time step t to the subsequent time steps t + 24 (i.e., the next 12 hours), with the assumption that perfect predictions are known in advance.",
    "Solar radiation is not included in the state-space despite the PV energy production is inherently dependent on this variable."
  ],
